---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Project Nirv">
  <main style="max-width: 720px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
      Project Nirv
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      A data-backed research project that turns verified sources into clear,
      simple and useful studies on markets, industries and business systems.
    </p>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What this is</h2>
      <p style="line-height: 1.6;">
        Project Nirv collects trusted reports, filings and datasets, then
        distills them into structured analysis. The goal is to cut noise and
        keep only the signal.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What’s coming</h2>
      <p style="line-height: 1.6;">
        Upcoming: industry deep dives, market maps and data notes that can be
        used as sources for operators, students and researchers.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
